# URL Canonicalization - Ensure all variations redirect to canonical URL
# Canonical URL: https://ctrl-build.com/

# Redirect www to non-www (multiple variations for Cloudflare Pages)
https://www.ctrl-build.com https://ctrl-build.com 301
https://www.ctrl-build.com/* https://ctrl-build.com/:splat 301
http://www.ctrl-build.com https://ctrl-build.com 301
http://www.ctrl-build.com/* https://ctrl-build.com/:splat 301

# Force HTTPS (should be handled by Cloudflare, but adding for safety)
http://ctrl-build.com https://ctrl-build.com 301
http://ctrl-build.com/* https://ctrl-build.com/:splat 301

# SEO redirects
/home / 301
/portfolio /work 301
